{"tid":983539,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［硬件撚］討論硬件知識、砌機list、解答問題集中帖（143）","createTime":"2019-01-16T04:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T12:12:55.000Z","uid":139070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f99c7f27281f75ae075c6cfc3ba18668517e57dd","tid":983539,"uid":139070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新人求List需知</span></span><br />\n<br />\n為方便連登眾巴絲可以幫助你，請你合作<br />\n不但可以令連登眾巴絲可以盡快回覆你的問題，更可以令條List更適合你所需<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">關於所有店舖事項請巴打從其他有效方式聯絡 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">顯卡係蝗語，請講顯示卡或display card </span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9Li1671.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9Li1671.gif&h=e2849c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. Budget<br />\nNO MONEY NO TALK ，預算上限寬鬆可以買好一點，預算太低可能要將就或繼續儲錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFQCM1P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFQCM1P.gif&h=c0d97530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打機INTEL<br />\n多工AMD</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦主要用途<br />\n你想玩咩遊戲? (多數砌機都會打機，如果唔係請另外講明)<br />\n最好講game名，唔好一句Steam game/blizzard/EA game就算<br />\n因為成千上萬隻人地唔知你玩邊隻<br />\n需唔需要直播或錄製遊戲影片?<br />\n<br />\n3. 個人需求<br />\n玩以上遊戲你最低可接受嘅畫質(Ultra/高/中/低)?最低可接受幾fps?<br />\n如果你預計會玩新遊戲，想幾耐唔駛升級電腦硬件?<br />\n想唔想超頻?散熱需求如何?使唔使靜過Dyson?<br />\n有冇特定嘅牌子信仰?想唔想有華麗嘅RGB光效?<br />\n<br />\n4. 現在或將會使用mon的類型<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">解像度</span>有分1080p, 2K(1440p), 4K(2160p)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">更新頻率</span>有分60Hz, 144Hz, 240Hz<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">畫面比例</span>有分 16:9, 21:9, 32:9<br />\n你想要咩解像度(畫質)同更新頻率(流暢度)?<br />\n解像度高，會對打機效能造成影響，但畫質會更好<br />\n更新頻率高，如效能足夠可以造成比低更新頻率更好嘅流暢度<br />\n<br />\n5. 自己都學習一些<br />\n講真，班巴絲好憎伸手黨，所以建議你行多一兩步<br />\n哪怕你直接照抄悠二巴打List放上黎問，佢地都會出手幫助<br />\n只係Ctrl-C和Ctrl-V咁簡單，大家都會開心嘅事點解唔做呢?<br />\n甚至可能你在過程中已經搵到需要的答案都不一定!<br />\n(悠二List網站 : <a href=\"http://yujihw.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com&d=SX%2BUoBDMe9%2BAxfAiwDzPbKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=0631680a\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n6.  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><del>大腦</del>Google係一樣很有用的東西</span></span><br />\n<br />\n7. 火牛： 平 Antec  貴 corsair RMx OR Evga G2/G3/P2/T2<br />\n<br />\n8. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請上銅柱,重覆檢查插好power,hdd led pin,HD AUDIO,MB 24PIN,usb2.0/3.0,fan pin(cpu,cha) or 3pin 4pin</span></span><br />\n<br />\n9. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>走線</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>走線</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>走線</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">走線未呀茶包</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n10. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">召喚硬件傳心師</span></span><br />\n冇人知你部機咩spec 呀<br />\n你有咩壞野問題唔該貼返full spec<br />\nCPU, MB, RAM, DISPLAY CARD, PSU etc.<br />\n如果開唔到機請附上機箱內部圖片一張<br />\n（<span style=\"color: red;\">走好線先</span>）<br />\n<br />\n11.<br />\n邊到買野好？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><del>HJ2Q</del></span> 3C1J<br />\n黃金：中央田 CentralField<br />\n黃金：正都 Capital<br />\n黃金：匯訊 Comdex<br />\n旺電：珍寶 Jumbo<br />\n<br />\n網店：<br />\nfaroll (悠二白汁腸)<br />\nhkterminal<br />\n飛馬電腦 <br />\n<br />\n海外：<br />\n新蛋 NewEgg<br />\n美馬 Amazon<br />\n<br />\n12.<br />\n拆cpu cooler 前記得整熱部機<br />\nAmd 拔劍有事幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n13.<br />\nH310 A320 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係冇budget 先考慮<br />\n<br />\n14.<br />\nCooler Master 不是好東西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見親都係叫你轉嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n15. 買咩箱好 (FD 教軍)<br />\nItx: Node 202, Silverstone RVZ 系列, inwin A1<br />\nMatx: Define Mini C<br />\nAtx: Define C 有d 錢多HDD 就再上 Define R6 <br />\n<br />\n16. For Advance Information<br />\nvrm 資料<br />\namd : <a href=\"https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/pga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hardwareluxx.de%2Fcommunity%2Ff12%2Fpga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html&d=SX%2BUoBDMe9%2BAxfAiwDzPbKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=eb1eb6cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/pga-am4-mainboard-vrm-liste-1155146.html</a><br />\nintel : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/lga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hardwareluxx.de%2Fcommunity%2Ff12%2Flga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html&d=SX%2BUoBDMe9%2BAxfAiwDzPbKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=90d14470\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hardwareluxx.de/community/f12/lga-1151-mainboard-vrm-liste-1175784.html</a><br />\n<br />\n有咩要加再同1001講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a82a39394607ab73bf903365a9a743b35ecec68c","tid":983539,"uid":139070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"就咁引左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌，是但啦"},{"pid":"4b2b9d5234479588961dc06482a16a2b75f26a20","tid":983539,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今朝部腦死左，power 制冇反應，肯定左唔係psu出事，今晚有排試邊道有問題"},{"pid":"9327b42dc2bed3cb9042e963a08f89dee055be10","tid":983539,"uid":139070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"再開左，此post 已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ca6a740016596347db640405f32075eb886e50","tid":983539,"uid":57819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T07:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XraVZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XraVZO.jpg&h=f9575005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己諗左條list，想問下各位意見，感謝<br />\n主要用黎打機，玩之後既Bio RE2﹑battlefield V等fps遊戲<br />\n會直播/錄製遊戲影片<br />\nbuget大約15K<br />\n而家條list有冇咩改善（機箱冇加入去，打算到時睇）<br />\n煙佬 2080係咪要改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0d22b2c818cb7a8e5212852cd7a37cad7dd978","tid":983539,"uid":6328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"CPU\tIntel&reg; Core&trade; Coffeelake i3-8100<br />\nMotherboard\tASUS PRIME H310M-E R2.0<br />\nRAM\tADATA Premier 8GB (1 x 8GB) DDR4 2666 Mhz C19<br />\nHDD\tWD Blue WD10EZEX 1TB<br />\nSSD\tKingston A400 Series 240GB SATA 3<br />\nCase\tAeroCool Corporate Series CS-102 Micro-ATX<br />\nPSU\tAcBel iPower G Series G-450 450W<br />\n<br />\n如果靜係想執相 唔會剪片打機<br />\n呢部夠唔夠做 ？"}]}